      <td width="800" style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size:18px; color:#222223; border-left:1px solid #ACACAC; border-right:1px solid #ACACAC; padding-left:38px; padding-top:25px; padding-right:38px"><table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" bordercolor="" width="100%" bgcolor=""><tr><td><table  width="100%" bgcolor="#ffffff" border="0" bordercolor="" cellpadding="5" cellspacing="0"><tr><td style="font-family:Arial; font-size:13px"><p id="text-placeholder" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;">
<font size="2"><font face="Arial">Dear&nbsp;</font>Kerry<font face="Arial">,</font></font>
</p>
<p id="text-placeholder" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;">
<font face="Arial" size="2"><br />
</font>
</p>
<p id="text-placeholder" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;">
<font face="Arial" size="2">We are pleased to announce that we are establishing <b>Brookfield Senior Real Estate Finance Fund</b> (&ldquo;<g class="gr_ gr_56 gr-alert gr_spell gr_run_anim gr_inline_cards ContextualSpelling ins-del multiReplace" id="56" data-gr-id="56">BSREF</g>&rdquo; or the &ldquo;Fund&rdquo;) as Brookfield&rsquo;s primary open-end private vehicle to invest in U.S. senior commercial real estate floating rate debt.&nbsp;</font>
</p>
<p id="text-placeholder" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;">
<font face="Arial" size="2"><br />
</font>
</p>
<p id="text-placeholder" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;">
<font face="Arial" size="2"><g class="gr_ gr_67 gr-alert gr_spell gr_run_anim gr_inline_cards ContextualSpelling ins-del multiReplace" id="67" data-gr-id="67">BSREF</g> is a natural extension of the real estate finance strategy that Brookfield has successfully executed over the past 14 years. The Fund will seek to invest in real <g class="gr_ gr_68 gr-alert gr_spell gr_run_anim gr_inline_cards ContextualSpelling ins-del multiReplace" id="68" data-gr-id="68">estate related</g> transactions in a credit risk position that is (i) senior to traditional equity and junior mezzanine debt and (ii) subordinate to senior debt, with a focus on senior mezzanine loans secured by properties in major U.S. metropolitan markets.&nbsp;</font>
</p>
<p id="text-placeholder" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;">
<font face="Arial" size="2"><br />
</font>
</p>
<p id="text-placeholder" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;">
<font face="Arial" size="2"><g class="gr_ gr_55 gr-alert gr_spell gr_run_anim gr_inline_cards ContextualSpelling ins-del multiReplace" id="55" data-gr-id="55">BSREF</g> is targeting a net internal rate of return of 6-7%, with current income as the major component of return.<sup>1,2</sup></font>
</p>
<p id="text-placeholder" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;">
<font face="Arial" size="2"><br />
</font>
</p>
<p id="text-placeholder" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;">
<font face="Arial" size="2">Key features of the Fund include:</font>
</p>
<p id="text-placeholder" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;">
</p>
<ul style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px;">
		
	<li><font size="2"><b>Established Track Record. </b>Over $3.9 billion of capital deployed in real estate finance transactions within the last 12 years.<br />
		&nbsp;</font></li>	
	<li><font size="2"><b>Integrated Investment and Operating Platforms. </b>Brookfield&rsquo;s operating businesses is expected to provide the Fund with several competitive advantages, namely: (i) enhanced underwriting based on real-time market data; (ii) active asset management, including, if necessary, operating capacity in default situations; and (iii) a compelling combination of real estate and financial expertise.<br />
		&nbsp;</font></li>	
	<li><font size="2"><b>Experienced Leadership. </b>Managed by the same team that has been successfully investing in commercial real estate credit at Brookfield since 2002.</font></li>
</ul>
<p style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px;">
</p>
<p id="text-placeholder" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;">
<font face="Arial" size="2"><br />
</font>
</p>
<p id="text-placeholder" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;">
<font size="2">For more information, please refer to the&nbsp;<a href="http://cl.S7.exct.net/?qs=7dee24c47ddd16b17021c20a279832f7becdaa9514667bbfd7dee8437a8768c1bb8026345c21db16b3159792d290a203e4f1e968a5f4fe08" title="Fund presentation"  >Fund presentation</a>. <font face="Arial">We appreciate the opportunity to discuss in further detail with you. Please contact me if you have questions or would like to arrange a meeting.</font></font>
</p>
<p id="text-placeholder" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;">
<font face="Arial" size="2"><br />
</font>
</p>
<p id="text-placeholder" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;">
<font face="Arial" size="2">Thank you.&nbsp;</font>
</p>
<p style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;">
<font face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 13px;">&nbsp;</span></font>
</p>
<p style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;">
<font face="Arial"><font face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 13px;">&nbsp;</span></font></font>
</p>
<p style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;">
